This plan adds a Stepper compound component to the shadcn/ui v4 component library. The Stepper follows the established custom-context compound component pattern exemplified by `carousel.tsx`, with a nested item context pattern similar to `form.tsx`. It requires creating 2 new files and modifying 2 registry files.

